lead_paragraph: Trade Talks Are Called Test of U.S. Leadership The White House is regarding the global trade talks that are beginning today in Doha, Qatar, as a test of leadership in the war on terrorism, while other countries have their own agendas. PAGES C1, W1 Bush Rebuked by Saudi The Saudi foreign minister criticized the president for refusing to meet with Yasir Arafat. PAGE A8
